{
  "stem": "935.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they kept dancing and singing were very merry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whatever political mess, you know, took place behind the doors, nobody paid any attention to it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nobody I knew did either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was still propaganda.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A lot of propaganda.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You heard rumors and more rumors and more rumors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But life went on in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, you have to realize as far as I'm concerned, Vienna was-- Austria was always anti-Semitic, but never obvious.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- not me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no dealings with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no dealings with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you can have a sore on your hand and you learn to live with it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You don't pay attention to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's there, but you know it's there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It doesn't hurt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It doesn't bother you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It doesn't cost you any inconveniences, but it's there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It shouldn't be there, but it's there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this is what it was with Austria, always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then on-- it went on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I studied for the state exam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I studied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And again, I didn't see any Nazis in Vienna, nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For the time I was there, I didn't see any of it, none of it at all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And whatever-- if my mother knew more about it, she certainly wouldn't have told me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Even my sister would have been exposed to it, which I don't think she was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She wouldn't have told me, either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I certainly didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sat home brooding about Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't sit home brooding about the Nazis, because I wouldn't have understood who the hell are the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What is Nazi?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's something you can't really-- you can't focus on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Were you ashamed?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
